{
  "texts": [
    "We discuss here the conventional target identification approaches with a focus on the application of AI algorithms to target identification.",
    "This paper aims to offer a progressive outlook on the emergence of the AI-driven drug discovery era and encourage the integration of AI technologies into drug discovery pipelines.",
    "Strategies in target identification: from experiments to machine learning Target identification can be classified into three distinct strategiesexperimental, multiomic, and computational approaches.",
    "Using these methods collaboratively can generate novel therapeutic hypotheses in exploratory target identification, thus significantly enhancing our understanding of complex diseases.",
    "The emergence of artificial intelligence (AI) in early drug development."
  ]
}